  <brief_title>Effect of Exosomes Derived From Red Blood Cell Units on Platelet Function and Blood Coagulation</brief_title>
  <official_title>In Vitro Study of the Effect of Exosomes Derived From Red Blood Cell Units on Platelet Function and Blood Coagulation in Healthy Volunteers' Blood</official_title>
  <sponsors>
